(firstQuint)Observational Study With NOVOCART Inject in the Reconstruction of the Hip Joint With Full Thickness Cartilage Defects.

 Prospective and multicenter non-interventional study to evaluate safety and efficacy of NOVOCART(R) Inject in patients with impingement syndrom in the hip.

 Safety: 24-month post treatment follow up period by measuring the number of adverse drug reactions/serious adverse drug reactions.

 Efficacy: 24-month post treatment follow up period using iHOT 33 and EuroQuol-5D-5L.

